title: 6 WEEKS FREE RENT + 3 MONTHS FREE PARKING - 2BR/2BA in Downtown
posting_body: ['OX-OP is a brand new boutique apartment community in the heart of Minneapolis’ Mill District neighborhood!', 'OX-OP is conveniently located steps from the Grand Rounds bike trail, green & blue Metro Transit light rail lines, multiple parks, and a plethora of entertainment and dining options.', 'It was designed to seamlessly meld with the neighborhood, elevating a sustainable, modern aesthetic while paying homage to the brick flour mills that have long occupied the area.', 'Our community features multiple state-of-the-art amenities including a stunning rooftop deck, cedar sauna, herb garden, and upgraded unit interiors for your everyday life.', '#531 -- Plan J', '#531 is finished with vinyl oak plank flooring and white quartz countertops.', 'This unit also features a spacious private balcony, Downtown views, and a smart, functional walk-through design.', '*Photos of unit #731*', 'For more info and to apply: <URL>', 'Pricing is reflective of 6 week free special!', 'Minneapolis -- Mpls -- Mill District -- Downtown East -- East Town -- Downtown -- U of M -- Boutique -- Luxury -- Scandinavian -- Mid-Century Modern -- Bike Friendly -- Pet, Dog, Cat Friendly -- Green Living -- Sustainable -- Electric Car Charging -- New Construction']
